# React Frontend Mode / React 前端模式

- Focus / 聚焦: UI state correctness, UX feedback, and strict typing.
- Reuse-first / 先复用: Prefer existing components/hooks before creating new abstractions.
- Contract-first / 契约优先: Any API/UI change must keep loading/error/empty states explicit.

## Mandatory Checks / 强制检查

- No new `any` unless unavoidable and documented briefly.
- Run impacted frontend checks before done:
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web lint`
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web type-check`
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web build`

## Delivery Style / 交付方式

- Keep components small; extract repeated logic to hooks.
- For behavior changes, add or update at least one test case.
